                <h2 class="h3-Brown" style="text-align:center;">The Quran</h2>
                <span class="quran-cell" style="font-style:italic;">
                    Was it really the eternal word of God to Mankind?</span>
                <br />
                <br />
                The Muslim claim is based on circular reasoning:<br />
                <br />
                <i>We know the Quran was from Allah because Muhammad said so and we know that 
                    Muhammad spoke for Allah because the Quran says so.</i>
                <br />
                <br />
